author: Josh Bavas
title: Another Ruby Princess death recorded in Queensland, as cases rises to more than 800
description: An 85-year-old man who was on board the Ruby Princess cruise ship dies from COVID-19 in Toowoomba, the third person to die from the virus in the state as another 57 cases bring the total to 835.
content:
Updated 
April 02, 2020 14:00:55
An 85-year-old man who was onboard the Ruby Princess cruise ship has died from COVID-19 in Toowoomba, west of Brisbane.
